{"tid":1170093,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"上t=Ted講Talk 王梓軒分享追夢：「莫忘初衷」","createTime":"2019-05-24T19:46:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-25T05:00:16.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ea56ee5269e8fcac3421b9171d0c7eb7719f9bde","tid":1170093,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T19:46:36.000Z","msg":"上個月王梓軒為音樂舞台劇《利瑪竇》忙得不可開交，日前，梓軒為美國著名講座到恒生管理學院演講，主題是「Looking Forward」，並分享自己「追夢」的過程，今次有9位演講者，他們來自不同行業，有著名Youtuber Torres Pit (托哥)、企業家Andrew Chambers、建築師David Nesbitt、銀行家及教育工作者Dannie Cheung、更生人士Jeffrey Andrews等等。<br />\n當日梓軒演講詞講述的重點為莫忘初衷：「BB時乜都想做、乜都想試，但往往父母或長輩怕你受傷害而阻止，長大後，亦會遵循父母嘅教導，畢業後去銀行返工&hellip;&hellip;之後我轉行做創作歌手，身邊人會有好多唔同嘅聲音，叫你唔好做，因為怕你辛苦，怕你條路難行，有時呢啲阻力會令你減低自信，又會令你懷疑自己能力等等&hellip;&hellip;所以要多謝一直鼓勵以及俾機會我嘅前輩及監製。」<br />\n接著梓軒又分享剛演完舞台劇《利瑪竇》，他被這位傳教士嘅經歷影響了不少，其傳教嘅精神也令他深明堅持自己目標嘅重要性，梓軒話：「一個意大利神父遠道去中國傳教，雖然最終達唔到自己最初建立嘅目標，但其傳教嘅經歷對學術研究、文化交流都有好大貢獻！」梓軒呼籲學生們每遇到困難都不要輕易放棄，要堅持、繼續前行，千萬不要忘記自己嘅初衷！<br />\n雖然演講時間只有20分鐘，但梓軒花了不少時間準備，梓軒話：「兩個月前收到邀請，我就開始準備演講詞，希望我嘅經歷可以啟發到他人！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20190524/large/1558680873_000d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20190524%2Flarge%2F1558680873_000d.jpg&h=85e1ccf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20190524/large/1558677900_3b11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20190524%2Flarge%2F1558677900_3b11.jpg&h=f1d8c32b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20190524/large/1558677904_3004.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20190524%2Flarge%2F1558677904_3004.jpg&h=d31be5ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20190524/large/1558677940_b077.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20190524%2Flarge%2F1558677940_b077.jpg&h=59d068ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20190524/large/1558678014_f01a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20190524%2Flarge%2F1558678014_f01a.jpg&h=b5d8ec4b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4309d71969e1e41e9da424db8af6683ede3a98a5","tid":1170093,"uid":152123,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T19:55:27.000Z","msg":"憑咩"},{"pid":"23782de176bc06938ace637e5cc03a1687683f2e","tid":1170093,"uid":815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4309d71969e1e41e9da424db8af6683ede3a98a5","tid":1170093,"uid":152123,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T19:55:27.000Z","msg":"憑咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T20:05:37.000Z","msg":"憑老豆有錢"},{"pid":"c9c26b4f531e8013e159db8c89022a236f49f654","tid":1170093,"uid":52071,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T20:31:53.000Z","msg":"最後他成為偉大的數學家"},{"pid":"90074d80a99421f50e3df34a0c6fca6dc179c40f","tid":1170093,"uid":22694,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T20:35:13.000Z","msg":"我上網買條褲幾多錢？1、2、3！"},{"pid":"9b5c82dd7d93705e1193b2fa9d76b315f1428df3","tid":1170093,"uid":243854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T20:38:37.000Z","msg":"咁入面有勁人都要搵啲差嘅襯托返嘅"},{"pid":"6f074910633f6fe9e06e9c287f494d3015292d2c","tid":1170093,"uid":130105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4309d71969e1e41e9da424db8af6683ede3a98a5","tid":1170093,"uid":152123,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T19:55:27.000Z","msg":"憑咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T22:49:36.000Z","msg":"唔係呀，個個有個 &quot;x&quot; ，外國都係乜鳩人都講得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f0703c625cf40ddf98ccb9d12de25eae49c8778","tid":1170093,"uid":33524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T00:36:49.000Z","msg":"100x30=30000